{"word":"διοίχομαι","slug":"διοίχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διοίχομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-οιχήσομαι</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-οίχημαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:— <i>to be quite gone by</i>, of time, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: of persons, <i>to be clean gone, to have perished</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>periisse</el>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to be gone through, ended</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}